text:
Hey Ryanne! We've specialized in a lot of nutrition, medical condition, chiropractic, and dental content — but we've branched out a bit into other areas, including book writing and author marketing, financial freedom, and wellness-related e-commerce content.

_Definitely_ long-form specialization. We rarely produce content of fewer than 1200 words, although we do write some social and newsletter content for select clients. We do one-off projects from time to time, but most of our clients are on long-term contracts for monthly content creation (and it's my preference, for the most part).

Hopefully not a silly question, but when you say "looking for," do you mean in terms of clients or internal personnel? (I'm looking for both, haha!)
